{"517210":{"success":true,"data":{"type":"game","name":"Bad Pad","steam_appid":517210,"required_age":0,"is_free":false,"controller_support":"full","dlc":[1008670],"detailed_description":"<h1>Becloudead<\/h1><p>Try out the Holidays specials of our new game Becloudead, official Prologue demo coming soon!<br>If you like what you see, don't forget to wishlist!<br><br><a href=\"http:\/\/store.steampowered.com\/app\/1448210\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  id=\"dynamiclink_0\" >http:\/\/store.steampowered.com\/app\/1448210\/<\/a><\/p><br><h1>About the Game<\/h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\\m\/ MetalVania Platformer \\m\/<\/h2>Bad Pad is a old school platformer with metroidvania elements.<br><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/517210\/extras\/bpgif4.gif?t=1659054640\" \/><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/517210\/extras\/bpgif3.gif?t=1659054640\" \/><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features<\/strong><\/h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>Humorous story-line told in songs and animations, those buttons sure can sing!<br>    <\/li><li>Original guitar driven rock and metal soundtrack that will keep you pumped.<br>    <\/li><li>Over 12 hours of gameplay and 160 scenes to explore, metroidvania style.<br>    <\/li><li>Diverse gameplay with cart riding levels, submarine levels, spaceship levels and more.<br>    <\/li><li>10 epic boss levels.<br>    <\/li><li>In-game mini arcade games.<br>    <\/li><li>Cool pixel art graphics and a retro feel.<br>    <\/li><li>Tight controls and game mechanics + gamepad support.<br>    <\/li><li>Use of physics and changing gravity.<br>    <\/li><li>Environmental puzzles.<br>    <\/li><li>One item-based inventory system, hey a button doesn't have pockets, deal with it.<br>    <\/li><li>Three game difficulties to select from.<br>    <\/li><li>Lots of steam achievements.<\/li><\/ul><br>The wacky premise of Bad Pad is told in songs and is set around a gamepad's buttons who came to life, their endless battles, mind controlling machines and a little bit of time traveling.<br><br>Join Square in his adventures, survive Evil Pen's hellish castles, help save Hexa and Trapezoid and probably the rest of the world!<br><br>Give Bad Pad DEMO a try, it is always up-to-date and if you decide to buy to the full game you can continue playing with your saved progress.<br><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/517210\/extras\/bpgif5.gif?t=1659054640\" \/><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/517210\/extras\/bpgif2.gif?t=1659054640\" \/><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/517210\/extras\/steamReleaseSmall.png?t=1659054640\" \/>","about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\\m\/ MetalVania Platformer \\m\/<\/h2>Bad Pad is a old school platformer with metroidvania elements.<br><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/517210\/extras\/bpgif4.gif?t=1659054640\" \/><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/517210\/extras\/bpgif3.gif?t=1659054640\" \/><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features<\/strong><\/h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>Humorous story-line told in songs and animations, those buttons sure can sing!<br>    <\/li><li>Original guitar driven rock and metal soundtrack that will keep you pumped.<br>    <\/li><li>Over 12 hours of gameplay and 160 scenes to explore, metroidvania style.<br>    <\/li><li>Diverse gameplay with cart riding levels, submarine levels, spaceship levels and more.<br>    <\/li><li>10 epic boss levels.<br>    <\/li><li>In-game mini arcade games.<br>    <\/li><li>Cool pixel art graphics and a retro feel.<br>    <\/li><li>Tight controls and game mechanics + gamepad support.<br>    <\/li><li>Use of physics and changing gravity.<br>    <\/li><li>Environmental puzzles.<br>    <\/li><li>One item-based inventory system, hey a button doesn't have pockets, deal with it.<br>    <\/li><li>Three game difficulties to select from.<br>    <\/li><l